;Websites you use with Firefox can send you notifications in the background that can appear on screen or update the web page. You can control how these notifications appear and work.
Nuair a thadhlas tu air làrach ann am Firefox, tachraidh gun cuir e brathan thugad sa chùlaibh agus gun nochd iad sin air an sgrìn no gun ùraich iad an duilleag-lìn. ’S urrainn dhut smachd a chumail air na brathan seo.


;What is Push?
Dè tha ann am Push?


;Push is an optional feature that allows websites to send you messages even when you aren’t visiting the site.
’S e gleus roghainneil a tha ann am Push a bheir cead do làraichean-lìn brathan a chur thugad fiù mur eil thu air an làrach.


;Sites can use this feature to provide you with notifications or update data in the background.
Tha an gleus seo feumail do làraichean ach an urrainn dhut fios a chumail riut no dàta ùrachadh sa chùlaibh.


;For instance, a webmail site might use Push to provide you with a notification when new messages arrive, or a weather site might use Push to provide storm alerts.
Mar eisimpleir, ’s urrainn do làrach puist-lìn Push a chleachdadh ach an urrainn dha innse dhut nuair a gheibh thu teachdaireachd ùr no làrach aimsire airson rabhadh a chur thugad mun t-sìde.


;You will only receive messages from sites for which you have granted permission.
Chan fhaigh thu brathan ach o theachdaireachdan a thug thu cead dhaibh.


;How does it work?
Ciamar a dh'obraicheas e?


;Firefox maintains a connection to a push service.
Glèidhidh Firefox ceangal ri seirbheis push.


;Sites that you have granted permission for Push can use the service to send you messages.
Ma thug thu cead do làrach, ’s urrainn dha Push brathan a chur thugad slighe na seirbheise.


;Firefox delivers this push message to a small piece of JavaScript called a “worker”.
Libhrigidh Firefox am brath push seo do phìos beag de JavaScript air a bheil “obraiche”.


;The worker then processes the message.
Dèiligidh an t-obraiche ris a’ bhrath.


;It might decide to show a visual notification or store the message for later use.
Dh’fhaoidte gun nochd e brath lèirsinneach no gun glèidh e am brath airson a chur gu feum uaireigin eile.


;What information do I share with a site?
